                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#7v" facs="010">Fol. 7v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1024MosesLaw">Moses Receiving Law</ref> with caption <q>“His brother, Aaron, “Prophet Moses with his tablet,” and “His sister, Miriam.” On the book is written the Trinitarian formula</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#8r" facs="010">Fol. 8r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref> attended by the angels <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7049Michael">Michael</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4377Gabriel">Gabriel</persName></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#24v" facs="027">Fol. 24v</locus><desc>Jesus with the Apostles with caption <q>“The Twelve Apostles.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#25r" facs="027">Fol. 25r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1033Ascension">Ascension of Jesus</ref> with caption <q>"The ascension of Our Lord, Jesus Christ.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#44r" facs="046">Fol. 44r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1086StrikingHead">The Striking of the Head, ኵርዓተ፡ ርእሱ፡</ref> with caption <q>“The striking of the head.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#66v" facs="069">Fol. 66v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1049Resurrection">Resurrection of Jesus</ref> raising Adam and Eve. with caption <q>“With Eve,” “How Our Lord Jesus Christ rose from the dead on the third day,” and “With Adam.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#102v" facs="105">Fol. 102v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1099StMary">St Mary</ref> <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3725Elizabet">ʾElsābeṭ</persName> and Solome. The one on the right holding a book and the one of the left holding a book. with caption <q>“How the Virgin Mary Greeted Elizabeth.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#151v" facs="154">Fol. 151v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1114Gabriel"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: AT1114Gabriel</span></ref> The Angel Gabriel rescues the three young men in the fiery furnace. with caption <q>“Saint Gabriel.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d9">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#79v #84v" facs="082 087">folss. 79v, 84v, </locus> (haräg);
